	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64573831"><p><div class="quote"><p> Linux isn't really a viable competitor if you do anything but web programming. If you game, make music or stream content Linux has a host of limitations.</p></div><p>

For me, there's nothing I need Windows for that I can't do on Linux.  It's more the other way around.  I'm not saying Linux doesn't have limitations for certain things people do on Windows, but to say you can't do "anything but web programming" isn't my experience at all.  From my perspective, Windows is the OS with limitations.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64573831">

